data.description: Incredible duplex in the heart of Bluff Park. This property would be perfect for someone looking to houseback and live in one side of the property while renting it out the other side. Both units have 3 bedrooms, a bonus room, and 2 full bathroom with the master bedrooms on the main floor. The vacant side features a private pool and hot tub with additional space for entertaining. 2512 has been renting for 1800 while the owner has been living in the opposite side. Estimated rent for both sides is 4000 per month.
